{"tid":2439042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來霉根喺個訪談入面嘅指控 全部都係講大話！","createTime":"2021-03-09T03:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T07:20:37.000Z","uid":28114,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7567497d84b34793159dc3ca912fb36b326a836b","tid":2439042,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"反駁晒聲稱個仔冇銜頭、冇英國政府特別保護<br />\n<br />\nWas Meghan&rsquo;s son Archie denied the title &lsquo;prince&rsquo; because he&rsquo;s mixed race?<br />\nThe Duchess of Sussex told Oprah she was shocked at the decision &ndash; but who made it, and was it fair?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/mar/08/why-meghan-harry-son-archie-denied-title-prince-mixed-race\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2F2021%2Fmar%2F08%2Fwhy-meghan-harry-son-archie-denied-title-prince-mixed-race&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=d5fffef7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/mar/08/why-meghan-harry-son-archie-denied-title-prince-mixed-race</a><br />\n<br />\nWill Archie Harrison Mountbatten-Windsor ever be a prince?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://royalcentral.co.uk/uk/sussex/will-archie-harrison-mountbatten-windsor-ever-be-a-prince-2-156679/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Froyalcentral.co.uk%2Fuk%2Fsussex%2Fwill-archie-harrison-mountbatten-windsor-ever-be-a-prince-2-156679%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ea66b8df\" target=\"_blank\">https://royalcentral.co.uk/uk/sussex/will-archie-harrison-mountbatten-windsor-ever-be-a-prince-2-156679/</a><br />\n<br />\n原來事實係佢決定放棄個仔嘅伯爵銜頭<br />\n<br />\nHe is, however, entitled to be styled as the child of a Duke and use his father&rsquo;s subsidiary title &ndash; Earl of Dumbarton &ndash; becoming Lord Archie, The Earl of Dumbarton. However, shortly after his birth, his parents opted for him to not use subsidiary titles or alternate styles &ldquo;at this time.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nGeorge V&rsquo;s declaration sets out: &ldquo;The grandchildren of the sons of any such sovereign in the direct male line (save only the eldest living son of the eldest son of the Prince of Wales) shall have and enjoy in all occasions the style and title enjoyed by the children of dukes of this realm.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n而Extended members更加冇權享有英國政府特別保護<br />\n<br />\nExtended members of the royal family also do not have automatic right to police security, which is a matter the royal family never discusses. It is a decision made with the family, Home Office and Metropolitan police. Princess Eugenie and Princess Beatrice no longer have security paid for by the taxpayer."},{"pid":"b7e9032ea7e8a490ca00b7640e381fbaa86bf82f","tid":2439042,"uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"How Meghan and Harry's royal racism claims DIFFERED: Meghan said 'concerns over how dark baby's skin might be' were raised while she was pregnant but Harry said comments were before their marriage<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9338061/Did-Harry-Meghans-Royal-racism-claims-clash-two-hour-Oprah-chat.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-9338061%2FDid-Harry-Meghans-Royal-racism-claims-clash-two-hour-Oprah-chat.html&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=ddaad02f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9338061/Did-Harry-Meghans-Royal-racism-claims-clash-two-hour-Oprah-chat.html</a><br />\n一時又話結婚之前，一時又話結婚之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夾好口供未啊，好難捉摸啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Duchess of Sussex said 'concerns and conversations about how dark his skin might be when he's born' happened 'in those months when [I] was pregnant' with Archie.   <br />\n<br />\nBut later when Pr